Package: TrustVDJ
Title: Tools for Immune Repertoire Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person('Lianhao', 'Song', , 'hatsunecode@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'),
           comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-3211-3726'))
Description: A toolkit for read and prepare immune repertoire data. \code{TrustVDJ} package focuses on the reading and processing of TRUST4 and 10x software output results by using \code{ReadTrust} and \code{Read10x} functions, respectively. \code{TrustVDJ} also provides a convenience function \code{build_IMGT_reference} to download IMGT database reference and split it by species.
